rows.label: bf10230100_0010
rows.name: Long ago, in this world...

rows.label: bf10230100_0020
rows.name:
a struggle for survival incomparably greater than now
Was taking place.

rows.label: bf10230100_0030
rows.name: That sight was ugly, but also beautiful.

rows.label: bf10230100_0040
rows.name: What do humans live for?

rows.label: bf10230100_0050
rows.name: For whom?

rows.label: bf10230100_0060
rows.name: [ML:undisp]...

rows.label: bf10230100_0070
rows.name: For themselves.

rows.label: bf10230100_0080
rows.name:
To desire and to chase after things
is humanity's natural state.

rows.label: bf10230100_0090
rows.name: But I did not think that was good.

rows.label: bf10230100_0100
rows.name: I had lost hope in humanity.

rows.label: bf10230100_0110
rows.name: I sought a solution outside.

rows.label: bf10230100_0120
rows.name: One day, I discovered the Gate.

rows.label: bf10230100_0130
rows.name: Why it chose to appear before us, I do not know.

rows.label: bf10230100_0140
rows.name: But it held a certain possibility.

rows.label: bf10230100_0150
rows.name: Possibility?

rows.label: bf10230100_0160
rows.name: Our world is not the only one.

rows.label: bf10230100_0170
rows.name: Countless worlds exist, unaware of each other,

rows.label: bf10230100_0180
rows.name: overlapping and coexisting with one another.

rows.label: bf10230100_0190
rows.name:
The Gate was a connection
to those plural worlds.

rows.label: bf10230100_0200
rows.name: I opened that forbidden gateway

rows.label: bf10230100_0210
rows.name: believing that would change the world...
